Now that the election to the Parliament of the Land of Bavaria has passed, a union of BayernLB with the bank of the Land of Baden-Wuttenberg could materialize in the first.
For the Helaba, this is not particularly good news.
If the pressure that forces new mergers were to increase, the potential partners gradually escape him.
