Some children speak during the night.
I do not relate to those who wake up very awake by telling us something that happened the day before, but to children who speak during their sleep.
The first time this happens it may surprise you, but in reality it doesn’t matter.
It is a mild alteration of sleep called sleep.
This is quite common, especially in children and adolescents.
